{"tid":207595,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【歸咎性衝動】娶6個老婆生足54個 70歲司機：老婆病死 有仔女餓死","createTime":"2017-04-19T03:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T03:49:54.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17efe2cca693a7c58b314fe297a7d0f7380e2c4e","tid":207595,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170418/large/1492508898_f3e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170418%2Flarge%2F1492508898_f3e9.jpg&h=f0e7f38f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170418/large/1492498304_d491.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170418%2Flarge%2F1492498304_d491.jpg&h=69282a99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴基斯坦奎達市（Quetta）一名貨車司機可謂名副其實的「多仔公」，年屆70歲的他與6名妻子共誕54個孩子。他解釋如此多產，全因年青時的性衝動驅使－－每天都要做愛。<br />\n<br />\n門格爾（Abdul Majeed Mengal）其中12個孩子先後死亡，目前有22個兒子及20個女兒，長子巴里（Bari）已32歲，但大部份子女都未足10歲，最年幼的女兒只有2歲。門格爾共結過6次婚，第一位妻子是18歲時迎娶，其中2位妻子已逝世。他說﹕「我年青時體能很好，我每天都要做愛。」<br />\n當貨車司機的門格爾，每月最多只賺2.5萬巴基斯坦盧比（約1,800港元），要養大那麼多子女極不容易，加上他本來就家貧，導致不少子女是因吃不飽而死，「我其中一個妻子與孩子一起死亡，她患病，但我們沒有錢（治療），因此她死了，我失業而且無助。」<br />\n現時長子巴里亦步父親後塵做貨車司機，整個家族就靠他們兩人養活。由於經濟能力不許可，門格爾10名子女如今無錢上學，他稱：「我打工以確保大部份孩子可上學，我較年長的孩子雖已畢業，卻難以找到工作，我為他們提供教育，但無補於事，他們都失業，我祈求他們有工做。」<br />\n他強調雖然兒子眾多，但會透過參加家庭活動與42名子女及4名太太逐一溝通，因此一家人生活和諧。即使年事已高，他亦拒絕申領津貼，堅持靠自己雙手養活家人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170419/56578809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170419%2F56578809&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7r5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=81cd5f92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170419%2F56578809&h=55417686\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170419/56578809</a>"},{"pid":"4c36ce68270117fd903a4129f706708c72fe0ffb","tid":207595,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T03:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屈機..."},{"pid":"4001073d54c33fac6eafa4ad4a9ce6e306bdf07f","tid":207595,"uid":10621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T03:42:39.000Z","msg":"皇帝都無咁多仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c942820d1acc921a28a1da00ee7db5446de9a1bd","tid":207595,"uid":34308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T03:43:06.000Z","msg":"餓死左仔女仲講咩靠自己雙手養活家人"},{"pid":"7358844ec3e6bf6858cb279d0afb9213e27085ea","tid":207595,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"中學地理堂問題：點解發展中國家或地區，傾向生更多仔女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686e4d468a99238ec121d4343af84d8f097669da","tid":207595,"uid":10293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T03:48:20.000Z","msg":"真正餓死老婆瘟臭屋"},{"pid":"d16f18486fe524c30db025662d851d9d22b9241b","tid":207595,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T03:49:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學地理堂問題：點解發展中國家或地區，傾向生更多仔女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無野做咪扑<br />\n覺得養兒可以防老"}]}